name: 玛瑞莎·冯·布莱肯
name_full: 玛瑞莎·冯·布莱肯 Marissa Von Bleicken

last_movies.title: 欢乐合唱团：真人秀 第一季

introduction: Marissa is a native New Yorker. She has been acting for over 13 years, appearing in commercials and off-broadway productions. She was born on October 30, 1991. She describes her style as "tight, bright and globally inspired." She was eliminated in Tenacity, episode 6. She suffered from anorexia in the past. She is Russian and German. She attended Tantasqua Regional High School in Massachusetts. Marissa attended Pace University in New York City as a theatre major.
